1
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:46,780
=Auspicious Nobles=

2
00:00:47,580 --> 00:00:49,940
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:52,500
(Making Money, Making Money)

4
00:00:57,030 --> 00:00:57,840
What is this?

5
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,430
When you hired me, I told you

6
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:13,870
there are only four ways
things end between us.

7
00:01:15,560 --> 00:01:16,590
Weren't there three?

8
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,870
The fourth is

9
00:01:20,310 --> 00:01:21,680
if you have money but don't pay up,

10
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:22,680
you die.

11
00:01:24,350 --> 00:01:25,870
Take all the money. It's all yours.

12
00:01:42,950 --> 00:01:44,200
Brilliant as always.

13
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:45,790
The real jackpot is here.

14
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:48,580
(Silver notes)

15
00:01:52,350 --> 00:01:54,590
This is all that Zheng Yuanhe's fault.

16
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,200
If it weren't for him,

17
00:01:56,290 --> 00:01:57,710
my life wouldn't be this miserable.

18
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,590
I am incompetent.

19
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:06,640
These chronicle offices keep popping up.

20
00:02:07,000 --> 00:02:08,250
Please punish me, Your Highness.

21
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,080
A mere newspaper with a few poems

22
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:14,280
can amass fortunes out of thin air

23
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,120
and manipulate public trends.

24
00:02:17,710 --> 00:02:18,590
She even managed

25
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:20,800
to build herself up
as a revered great scholar,

26
00:02:21,590 --> 00:02:23,680
making me hesitant to strike.

27
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:27,870
Father is going to praise
my second brother again.

28
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,000
Not only that,

29
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:31,760
I just received a secret report

30
00:02:31,850 --> 00:02:32,800
saying the Second Prince

31
00:02:32,810 --> 00:02:34,390
is secretly contacting major merchants.

32
00:02:35,030 --> 00:02:35,960
It seems

33
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,520
he intends to hold

34
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,690
the Imperial Merchants Conference
at his residence.

35
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:43,150
The one who truly wants
to hold the conference

36
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:44,560
is the person behind him.

37
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,430
The foolish Yuanzhao

38
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,520
is merely a puppet in her hands.

39
00:02:49,750 --> 00:02:51,000
Your Highness, do you mean

40
00:02:51,750 --> 00:02:52,840
the Master of Wangshi Tower?

41
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:01,470
She wants to seize all financial power

42
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:03,470
and overthrow
the foundation of Great Yong.

43
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,560
I will never allow it.

44
00:03:07,590 --> 00:03:10,190
Isn't she enjoying
being in the limelight?

45
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,240
Then, I

46
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:16,470
will make sure
she never enjoys it again.

47
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,430
Hyah!

48
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:20,590
Hyah!

49
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:22,710
Hyah!

50
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:26,470
My right eyelid keeps twitching.

51
00:03:26,750 --> 00:03:28,150
I feel like something is wrong.

52
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,870
Whoa!

53
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,120
The scheming fool.

54
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,120
How dare he come after me so blatantly!

55
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:18,000
Defend the Tower Master to the death!

56
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,870
- Defend the Tower Master to the death!
- Defend the Tower Master to the death!

57
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,270
Why am I actually a bit moved?

58
00:04:25,630 --> 00:04:26,950
All my loyalty to you is here.

59
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,600
Leave no one alive.

60
00:04:29,600 --> 00:04:30,120
Attack!

61
00:04:30,510 --> 00:04:33,870
- Kill them!
- Kill them!

62
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:45,190
Jiuzhu, be careful!

63
00:05:06,510 --> 00:05:08,560
Since you only work
for her for the money,

64
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,120
I will offer you 500,000 taels.

65
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,680
Not everyone can buy me off.

66
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,390
I like her style.

67
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,430
As for you,

68
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:16,680
I don't.

69
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,160
Tower Master,

70
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:24,160
what happened?

71
00:05:24,170 --> 00:05:25,880
I was worried to death
when I got the letter.

72
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,800
Jiang Shuo, go get
the estate physician now.

73
00:05:28,810 --> 00:05:30,230
- Dare you ask?
- Yes, Your Highness.

74
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:32,590
I was almost hacked to death
on the road by your dear brother.

75
00:05:33,550 --> 00:05:34,390
Has everyone arrived?

76
00:05:34,820 --> 00:05:36,090
They are all inside awaiting you.

77
00:05:36,240 --> 00:05:37,070
Your injury...

78
00:05:37,070 --> 00:05:37,800
It won't kill me.

79
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,040
Just bandage it up quickly.

80
00:05:39,750 --> 00:05:40,190
Let's go.

81
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:41,570
Time to make some money off them.

82
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,360
Great.

83
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,600
Why hasn't the Tower Master arrived yet?

84
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,390
I can't wait to see the Tower Master.

85
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:47,950
Tower Master is here.

86
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:48,630
She's here.

87
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,720
She's here...

88
00:06:09,020 --> 00:06:10,140
Greetings, Tower Master.

89
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:12,460
Greetings, Your Highness.

90
00:06:12,660 --> 00:06:13,900
Let's cut to the chase.

91
00:06:14,100 --> 00:06:15,180
My Wangshi Chronicle

92
00:06:15,620 --> 00:06:18,180
can effortlessly make
your goods famous nationwide,

93
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,500
making everyone crave them.

94
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:20,940
On the other hand,

95
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,940
it can also make them notorious,

96
00:06:22,940 --> 00:06:24,300
leaving them despised by everyone.

97
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,420
This...

98
00:06:26,900 --> 00:06:28,860
Do you want to cooperate or not?

99
00:06:31,700 --> 00:06:33,180
What the Tower Master means...

100
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:35,700
She means using
the momentum of the newspaper

101
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:37,660
to help recommend your products.

102
00:06:38,460 --> 00:06:39,180
You only need

103
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:41,100
to purchase a space in the newspaper,

104
00:06:41,540 --> 00:06:43,900
and you can have
your firm's product information

105
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:45,220
published on it.

106
00:06:45,860 --> 00:06:46,780
In a single day,

107
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:49,660
it will spread to
all households across the capital.

108
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:52,980
It saves much more trouble
than shouting your wares.

109
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:54,740
Furthermore,

110
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:56,340
the Tower Master's style

111
00:06:56,460 --> 00:06:57,980
now leads the trends in the capital.

112
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:58,820
Everyone,

113
00:06:59,420 --> 00:07:01,020
do not miss this business opportunity.

114
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:02,150
That's right.

115
00:07:02,150 --> 00:07:02,620
Indeed.

116
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:04,260
Right now in the capital,

117
00:07:04,260 --> 00:07:06,740
everyone takes pride
in emulating the Tower Master.

118
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:09,180
There are huge profits to be made here.

119
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:10,340
At today's conference,

120
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:12,020
anyone who signs
a yearly framework agreement

121
00:07:12,020 --> 00:07:14,100
for newspaper advertising
with Wangshi Tower

122
00:07:14,740 --> 00:07:16,500
will have their ad fees
for the first month

123
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:17,980
completely waived.

124
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:19,300
Completely waived?

125
00:07:19,580 --> 00:07:21,940
This is a really rare opportunity.

126
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,740
A brilliant plan by the Tower Master.

127
00:07:23,780 --> 00:07:27,010
We are willing to follow
the Tower Master and the Second Prince.

128
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:30,980
We are willing to follow
the Tower Master and the Second Prince.

129
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:35,660
(Zhao Prince's Residence)

130
00:07:35,660 --> 00:07:36,900
This is a good business.

131
00:07:37,300 --> 00:07:38,060
Exactly.

132
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:40,020
Tower Master is truly brilliant.

133
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:43,140
Your Highness, we arrived late.

134
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,280
The Imperial Merchants
Conference is over.

135
00:07:44,300 --> 00:07:45,220
Farewell, Tower Master.

136
00:08:02,100 --> 00:08:03,620
(Not only did I come,)

137
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:06,020
(but I also made money
right in front of your face.)

138
00:08:06,540 --> 00:08:07,340
(Deal with it.)

139
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:41,340
Your Highness,

140
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:42,460
she is provoking you.

141
00:08:48,580 --> 00:08:50,540
She is asking for death.

142
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:59,980
Gold ingots...

143
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:03,100
Why are you pinging me?

144
00:09:11,280 --> 00:09:13,140
The monthly pay, including
the principal and interest,

145
00:09:13,140 --> 00:09:15,480
has been distributed to
the brothers without a penny short.

146
00:09:15,700 --> 00:09:18,540
Everyone also gets
an extra 200 taels as a bonus.

147
00:09:22,180 --> 00:09:22,940
This

148
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:25,220
is for you.

149
00:09:26,100 --> 00:09:29,220
Your exclusive top merit bonus
as my trusted chief official.

150
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,460
This is the back pay from last month.

151
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:38,060
What about this month?

152
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:43,380
Starting a business isn't easy.

153
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:45,900
Mainly, all the money
has been handed out.

154
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,060
Wait until next month.

155
00:09:48,220 --> 00:09:49,700
I'll make it up altogether next month.

156
00:09:49,780 --> 00:09:50,580
Handed out?

157
00:09:51,300 --> 00:09:53,620
Are you sure
that you didn't keep a secret stash?

158
00:09:55,980 --> 00:09:57,380
Of course not.

159
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:59,220
Am I that kind of person?

160
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:04,580
My sincerity toward the brothers
can be witnessed by heaven and earth.

161
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:10,300
(I have to hide some working capital
to guard against risks, right?)

162
00:10:14,500 --> 00:10:15,020
I'm leaving.

163
00:10:15,580 --> 00:10:16,500
Why are you leaving?

164
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:17,880
Your wound hasn't been dressed yet.

165
00:10:23,380 --> 00:10:25,700
How can you care so little
about your own body?

166
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:26,620
Sit down.

167
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:30,220
I will apply the medicine myself.

168
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:35,860
(Golden Sore Ointment)
Imperial Golden Sore Ointment.

169
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:36,990
Sponsored by the Second Prince.

170
00:10:37,540 --> 00:10:38,740
Do the brothers all have it?

171
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:39,620
Yes.

172
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:41,100
Caiyuan has already delivered it.

173
00:10:53,340 --> 00:10:54,620
Nice build.

174
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:57,980
You've got more substance
than my rice balls.

175
00:11:22,100 --> 00:11:24,460
Thank you all for saving me today.

176
00:11:25,740 --> 00:11:26,380
Don't worry.

177
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:28,900
In the future,
as long as I can make a living,

178
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:30,980
I will never treat you poorly.

179
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,500
When we make big money in the future,

180
00:11:33,850 --> 00:11:36,760
I'll get a beautiful wife
for every one of you.

181
00:11:37,540 --> 00:11:38,340
Why did you...

182
00:11:43,020 --> 00:11:43,580
I...

183
00:11:49,980 --> 00:11:50,500
You...

184
00:11:55,420 --> 00:11:56,140
I only want money.

185
00:11:56,880 --> 00:11:58,540
If you don't pay me
on time next month...

186
00:11:58,540 --> 00:11:59,220
I'll kill myself.

187
00:12:15,660 --> 00:12:19,620
Is it really that hard for me
to save some pocket money?

188
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:23,620
When will I ever reach this small goal?

189
00:12:27,860 --> 00:12:28,660
Tower Master,

190
00:12:29,620 --> 00:12:31,420
the Crown Prince
sent someone with a message.

191
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:34,020
He invites the Pan Residence
to attend the Spring Banquet.

192
00:12:35,380 --> 00:12:38,900
Is the jerk trying to check my wounds?

193
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:46,580
Here, Yang.

194
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:49,900
How does it taste?

195
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,900
(Could this be an ambush?)

196
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,860
The Crown Prince invited me here.

197
00:13:03,620 --> 00:13:05,060
Come, Yang.

198
00:13:05,060 --> 00:13:06,460
Taste the osmanthus wine here.

199
00:13:08,980 --> 00:13:09,620
Is it good?

200
00:13:10,020 --> 00:13:10,580
It's good.

201
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:12,990
- The Crown Prince has arrived.
- The Crown Prince's wine is, well...

202
00:13:17,700 --> 00:13:18,260
(Oh my.)

203
00:13:18,300 --> 00:13:19,900
(How much scented powder did he wear?)

204
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:23,690
- Greetings, Your Highness.
- Greetings, Your Highness.

205
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:24,860
It is freezing cold tonight.

206
00:13:25,060 --> 00:13:26,300
I have prepared a cloak for you.

207
00:13:46,860 --> 00:13:50,220
♪Snowflakes settle gently
upon your brows♪

208
00:13:50,980 --> 00:13:54,380
♪Your dark hair
brushes across my fingertips♪

209
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,900
♪Your smile♪

210
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:59,420
♪Melts away the winter snow♪

211
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:03,100
♪One fleeting glance says more
than a thousand words♪

212
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:06,900
♪Yet I stand before you♪

213
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:11,460
♪Unable to recognize your eyes♪

214
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:13,780
♪Though fate tries♪

215
00:14:13,780 --> 00:14:16,380
♪To make us pass each other by♪

216
00:14:16,580 --> 00:14:20,020
♪I choose to make our story whole♪

217
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:21,900
♪Though time slips by♪

218
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:23,660
♪As day turns into night♪

219
00:14:24,180 --> 00:14:28,220
♪I still remember
our days at Wangshi Tower♪

220
00:14:28,620 --> 00:14:31,020
♪One glance at you lasts a lifetime♪

221
00:14:31,020 --> 00:14:32,780
♪Blessed by fate♪

222
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:37,940
♪I believe this moment
will last forever♪

223
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:40,380
♪Your smiling face♪

224
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:43,220
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

225
00:14:43,220 --> 00:14:46,860
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

226
00:14:47,380 --> 00:14:50,820
♪And wander the world together♪

227
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:52,180
♪Holding you close♪

228
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:54,700
♪Envying neither lovers nor immortals♪

229
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:57,020
♪Your tenderness♪

230
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,900
♪Is the brightest moon♪

231
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:03,580
♪I'd rather
pledge three lifetimes to you♪

232
00:15:04,100 --> 00:15:07,420
♪Our love will never fade away♪

233
00:15:07,420 --> 00:15:09,860
♪Though heaven and earth grow old♪

234
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:14,660
♪My heart will remain forever pure♪

235
00:15:24,140 --> 00:15:26,300
♪Your smiling face♪

236
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:29,060
♪Is the most beautiful poem♪

237
00:15:29,380 --> 00:15:33,220
♪I'd rather spend my days with you♪

238
